Invoice Generator

bookmark_border
  • subject UI / UX
Description

Create a Invoice Generator using following details:-

  • There should be only one H1 tag with text "Invoice Generator".
  • There should be an HR tag below H1 tag.
  • There should be an empty SPAN tag with ID error below HR tag.
  • There should be a BR tag below SPAN tag.
  • There should be a DIV tag with ID add-item-section below BR tag and contains:-
  1. LABEL tag with text "Item name".
  2. INPUT tag below LABEL tag with following attributes:-
  3. ID should be item-name.
  4. TYPE should be TEXT.
  5. PLACEHOLDER should be "Enter item name".
  6. LABEL tag with text "Price" below INPUT tag.
  7. INPUT tag below LABEL tag with following attributes:-
  8. ID should be price.
  9. TYPE should be NUMBER.
  10. PLACEHOLDER should be "Enter price".
  11. LABEL tag with text "Discount" below INPUT tag.
  12. INPUT tag below LABEL tag with following attributes:-
  13. ID should be discount.
  14. TYPE should be NUMBER.
  15. PLACEHOLDER should be "Enter discount".
  16. BUTTON tag with ID add-item-button and TEXT "Add Item" below INPUT tag.
  • There should be an HR tag below DIV tag.
  • There should be a DIV tag with ID invoice-div below HR tag and contains:-
  1. An empty H2 tag with ID heading.
  • There should be a BR tag below DIV tag.
  • There should be a BUTTON tag with ID generate-invoice and TEXT "Generate Invoice".


Workflow:-

  • After CLICKING on the Add Item button the following things should happen:-
  1. If ITEM NAME is EMPTY than there should be an error "Please enter item name." show in SPAN (with ID error).
  2. If PRICE is EMPTY than there should be an error "Please enter price." show in SPAN (with ID error).
  3. If PRICE is NEGATIVE or NON-DECIMAL than there should be an error "Price should be non negative decimal number." show in SPAN (with ID error).
  4. If DISCOUNT is EMPTY than there should be an error "Please enter discount." show in SPAN (with ID error).
  5. If PRICE is NEGATIVE or NON-DECIMAL or GREATER THAN 100 than there should be an error "Discount should be decimal and in between (1-100)." show in (SPAN with ID error).
  6. If there is no any error than :-
  7. Set SPAN (with ID error) value "".
  8. Set text of H2 (with ID heading) as "All Items" .
  9. If DIV (with ID invoice-div) contain TABLE (with ID invoice-table) then remove it.
  10. If DIV (with ID invoice-div) not contain TABLE (with ID items-table) than add a TABLE (with ID items-table) contains.
  11. Add a TR contains 3 TH:-
  12. First TH have CLASS first-column with text "Item name".
  13. Second TH have CLASS center-column with text "Price (in INR)".
  14. Third TH have CLASS last-column with text "Discount (in %)".
  15. Add a new TR in TABLE (with ID items-table) contains 3 TD:-
  16. First TD have CLASS first-column contains VALUE of INPUT (with ID item-name).
  17. Second TD have CLASS center-column contains VALUE of INPUT (with ID price).
  18. Third TD have CLASS last-column contains VALUE of INPUT (with ID discount).
  19. EMPTY all INPUT VALUE.
  20. Set BUTTON (with ID generate-invoice) DISPLAY property INLINE BLOCK.
  • After CLICKING on the Generate Invoice button the following things should happen:-
  1. Set text of H2 (with ID heading) as "Invoice" .
  2. HIDE Generate Invoice button using DISPLAY.
  3. Remove TABLE (with ID items-table) from DIV (with ID invoice-div).
  4. Add TABLE with ID invoice-table in DIV (with ID invoice-div).
  5. Add a new TR in TABLE (with ID invoice-table) contains 6 TH :-
  6. First TH have CLASS first-column contains text "Item name".
  7. Second TH have CLASS center-column contains text "Price (in INR)".
  8. Third TH have CLASS center-column contains text "Discount (in %)".
  9. Fourth TH have CLASS center-column contains text "SGST".
  10. Fifth TH have CLASS center-column contains text "CGST".
  11. SIxth TH have CLASS last-column contains text "Final Price".
  12. For each ITEM create a new TR and add it to TABLE (with ID invoice-table) contains 6 TD.
  13. First TD have CLASS first-column contains ITEM NAME.
  14. Second TD have CLASS center-column contains PRICE.
  15. Third TD have CLASS center-column contains DISCOUNT.
  16. Fourth TD have CLASS center-column contains SGST.
  17. Fifth TD have CLASS center-column contains CGST.
  18. Sixth TD have CLASS first-column contains Final price.
  19. After add all items Add new TR in TABLE (with ID invoice-table) contains 6 TH.
  20. First TH have CLASS first-column contains text "Total".
  21. Second TH have CLASS center-column contains SUM of PRICE.
  22. Third TH have CLASS center-column contains SUM of DISCOUNT on all ITEMS (in INR).
  23. Fourth TH have CLASS center-column contains SUM of SGST on all ITEMS (in INR).
  24. Fifth TH have CLASS center-column contains SUM of CGST on all ITEMS (in INR).
  25. SIX TH have CLASS last-column contains SUM of FINAL PRICE.
  • SGST and CGST are 5% for all ITEMS.
  • FINAL PRICE should be calculated using following formula:-

discount_on_price = (price * discount) / 100

actual_price = price - discount_on_price

sgst = (actual_price * SGST) / 100

cgst = (actual_price * CGST) / 100

final_price = actual_price - sgst - cgst


Note:-

  • Initially there will be no any TABLE on webpage.
  • Initially Generate Invoice button should be hidden using DISPLAY.
  • BODY should have following properties:-
  1. TEXT should be in CENTER.
  2. BACKGROUND COLOR should be RGBA(26, 41, 48, 1).
  3. TEXT COLOR should be WHITE in RGBA format.
  • DIV (with ID add-item-section) should have following properties:-
  1. DISPLAY should be INLINE BLOCK.
  2. TEXT should be LEFT.
  3. PADDING should be 20PX.
  4. MARGIN TOP and BOTTOM should be 20PX.
  5. MARGIN LEFT and RIGHT should be 0PX.
  • All INPUT should have following properties:-
  1. DISPLAY should be BLOCK.
  2. MARGIN TOP and BOTTOM should be 14PX.
  3. MARGIN LEFT and RIGHT should be 0PX.
  4. BACKGROUND COLOR should be TRANSPARENT in RGBA format.
  5. TEXT SIZE should be 20PX.
  6. TEXT COLOR should be WHITE in RGBA format.
  7. BORDER
  • All LABEL should have following properties :-
  1. TEXT SIZE should be 18PX.
  2. TEXT WEIGHT should be 600.
  3. VERTICAL DISTANCE should be 22PX.
  4. TEXT should have WHITE(in RGB format) color SOLID UNDERLINE.
  • All BUTTON should have following properties:-
  1. BACKGROUND COLOR should be RGBA(255, 216, 56, 1).
  2. SOLID BORDER in WHITE COLOR ( in RGB format ) with 1PX SIZE.
  3. TEXT COLOR should be WHITE in RGBA format.
  4. TEXT SIZE should be 20PX.
  5. TEXT WEIGHT should be 600.
  • DIV (with ID invoice-div) should have following properties:-
  1. DISPLAY should be INLINE BLOCK.
  2. MARGIN TOP and BOTTOM should be 20PX.
  3. MARGIN LEFT and RIGHT should be 0PX.
  • TABLE and TR should have SOLID BORDER in WHITE COLOR ( in RGB format ) with 1PX SIZE.
  • TD and TH should have following properties:-
  1. SOLID BORDER in WHITE COLOR ( in RGB format ) with 1PX SIZE.
  2. PADDING should be 10PX.
  • CLASS first-column should have TEXT in LEFT.
  • CLASS center-column should have TEXT in CENTER.
  • CLASS last-column should have TEXT in RIGHT.
  • BUTTON (with ID generate-invoice) should have following properties:-
  1. DISPLAY should be NONE.
  2. BOTTOM MARGIN should be 50PX.
  • SPAN (with ID error) should have RGBA(228, 64, 3) TEXT COLOR.
